*Slatki* kolači su najbolje poslastica. (The *sweet* pastries are the best treat.)

Naši domaći *slatkiši* su najukusniji. (Our homemade *sweets* are the most delicious.)

*Slatkim* slovima reči je obradovala. (She was delighted with the *sweet* words.)

Volim da kupujem *slatko* voće. (I like to buy *sweet* fruit.)

Žudim da uživam u *slatkim* trenucima. (I crave to enjoy *sweet* moments.)